Sign up for an Office 365 tenant
E3 trial, Developer program, or Full blown demo 

Create app catalog site 
SharePoint Admin Center > Apps > Create > App Catalog > Title: Apps > /sites/apps 

Create a new Developer Site collection
SharePoint Admin Center > Sites > New > Developer > /sites/dev 

Access the SharePoint Workbench 
../sites/dev/_layouts/workbench.aspx

